      "content": "but there's no point in talking to a counselor or anything. they just don't get it. it's not just one person, it feels like the whole world has already decided i'm a joke. they won't stop. no matter what i do, the feeling just stays the same. i feel like i'm trapped in this nightmare and there's no way out.",
