      "content": "it's just exhausting. what's the point of even trying to fix things when everything feels so permanent? like, the bullying, the way people look at me... it's just how my life is now. people keep saying it gets better but it feels like things are just getting worse. i just want to find a way to make it all just... stop. to just be at peace without all this noise.",
